<style>
        #output-content, #output-content > p, #output-content > div {
            margin: 0;
            word-wrap: break-word;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: normal;
            font-style: normal;
            font-stretch: normal;
            line-height: 1.71;
            letter-spacing: normal;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        #output-content, #output-content > p > p, #output-content > div > div, #output-content > p > div, #output-content > div > p {
            text-align: unset;
        }

        .section_title, .provision_title, #output-content > .section_title, #output-content > .provision_title {
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        #output-content > table,
        li > table {
            width: 100% !important;   
            max-width: 100%;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-spacing: 0px;
            border: 1px solid #333 !important;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        #output-content > table > tbody > tr > td,
        li > table > tbody > tr > td {
            border: 1px solid #333 !important;
            border-left: 0px !important;
            border-top: 0px !important;
        }
        
        #output-content > table > tbody > tr > td:first-child,
        li > table > tbody > tr > td:first-child {
            border-right: 1px solid #333 !important;
        }

        #output-content > table > tbody > tr:last-child > td,
        li > table > tbody > tr:last-child > td {
            border-bottom: 0px !important;
        }

        #output-content > table > tbody > tr:nth-last-child(2) > td[rowspan="2"],
        #output-content > table > tbody > tr:nth-last-child(3) > td[rowspan="3"],
        #output-content > table > tbody > tr:nth-last-child(4) > td[rowspan="4"],
        #output-content > table > tbody > tr:nth-last-child(5) > td[rowspan="5"],
        li > table > tbody > tr:nth-last-child(2) > td[rowspan="2"],
        li > table > tbody > tr:nth-last-child(3) > td[rowspan="3"],
        li > table > tbody > tr:nth-last-child(4) > td[rowspan="4"],
        li > table > tbody > tr:nth-last-child(5) > td[rowspan="5"] {
            border-bottom: 0px !important;
        }

        #output-content > table > tbody > tr > td > p, #output-content > table > tbody > tr > td > div,
        #output-content > table > tbody > tr > td,
        li > table > tbody > tr > td > p, li > table > tbody > tr > td > div,
        li > table > tbody > tr > td {
            text-align: inherit;
            text-align-last: unset !important;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        #output-content > ol {
            padding-left: 35px;
        }
        
        ol {
            margin: 0px;
            padding-left: 25px;
            text-indent: 0px;
        }

        ol > li {
            font-weight: normal;
        }
        
        td[rowspan] {
            position: relative;
        }
        
        td[rowspan]:before {
            position: absolute;
            content: "";
            top: -1px;
            left: -1px;
            background-color: transparent;
            border: solid black 1px;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }
        
        td[colspan] {
            position: relative;
        }
        td[colspan]:before {
            position: absolute;
            content: "";
            top: -1px;
            left: -1px;
            background-color: transparent;
            border: solid black 1px;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }

        @media print {
            p.page-break {
                page-break-before: always;
            }
        }
